headline: Otis New Equipment Project Wins Industry Award
summary: Elevator World magazine has selected an Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) project as a winner in its annual Project of the Year awards – recognizing its deep expertise and experience serving airports and major infrastructure projects.
